  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Zero Aim, 100% Bullet Hell!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282610/extras/bdc060218f6a24ec77f6808c5bf0bffa.poster.avif?t=1773945946\" width=800 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282610/extras/bdc060218f6a24ec77f6808c5bf0bffa.webm?t=1773945946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282610/extras/bdc060218f6a24ec77f6808c5bf0bffa.mp4?t=1773945946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BitBattle </strong>is a 2D multiplayer action shooter.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, Shoot, Jump and Shoot again! What counts is your reaction time and your skill. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect weapons and items to make your opponent's life even worse.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282610/extras/98c30a2ad69b566e6e67d8be25e79091.poster.avif?t=1773945946\" width=1072 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282610/extras/98c30a2ad69b566e6e67d8be25e79091.webm?t=1773945946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282610/extras/98c30a2ad69b566e6e67d8be25e79091.mp4?t=1773945946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282610/extras/f4d36c9a9a0e2c40726b0dae9ae3c2db.poster.avif?t=1773945946\" width=1072 height=402 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282610/extras/f4d36c9a9a0e2c40726b0dae9ae3c2db.webm?t=1773945946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282610/extras/f4d36c9a9a0e2c40726b0dae9ae3c2db.mp4?t=1773945946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282610/extras/1ef575244faaf56c3f2ecd7a0528bd43.poster.avif?t=1773945946\" width=818 height=636 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282610/extras/1ef575244faaf56c3f2ecd7a0528bd43.webm?t=1773945946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282610/extras/1ef575244faaf56c3f2ecd7a0528bd43.mp4?t=1773945946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiplayer up to 4 Players </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Couch Coop up to 4 Players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Different Maps </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Different Weapons </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Different Items</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282610/extras/285faa8d51d22ff691ede32762e0aceb.poster.avif?t=1773945946\" width=1072 height=402 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282610/extras/285faa8d51d22ff691ede32762e0aceb.webm?t=1773945946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets